    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta check out this absolute beauty! Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it\u2019s looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. It\u2019s spotless inside and out and drives like a dream. If you're looking for something that's practically perfect, this is the one! Come say hi and take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
