      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, maintained in absolute showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, glass-like finish with zero rock chips or swirl marks, protected by a professional ceramic coating that makes the paint pop. Inside, the cabin remains pristine, retaining that original new-car scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of wear on the bolsters, and every electronic component and switch functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a comprehensive folder of service records included. This is a meticulously preserved example of automotive excellence, offering a driving experience that feels as fresh as the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
