      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to say goodbye to this beauty, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely stunning condition\u2014seriously, it looks and drives just like it did the day it left the showroom! It\u2019s been pampered and kept spotless, so if you\u2019ve been looking for that perfect ride that feels brand new, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come by and see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019re going to fall in love at first sight!",
