    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW M-Division engineering, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This vehicle is in pristine, collector-grade condition, having received exhaustive preventative maintenance including a rod bearing service, a comprehensive VANOS overhaul with Beisan components, and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides precise, mechanical shift throws, while the variable M-differential lock ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The suspension maintains its factory-fresh damping characteristics with no evidence of bushing fatigue. The exterior finish is impeccable, showing uniform paint depth across all panels and no signs of thermal cycling or environmental wear in the engine bay.",
